{"tid":1561033,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"民主派動議譴責警方毆打大埔少年 建制派離席觸發流會","createTime":"2019-09-11T12:28:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T15:55:12.000Z","uid":68738,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1e18e35e77ce4593254a92023f70aa45e66ee719","tid":1561033,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:28:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190911/large/1568189955_7c77.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190911%2Flarge%2F1568189955_7c77.png&h=be9d5752&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新同盟周炫瑋提出「譴責警方7/9於大埔墟港鐵站毆打及拘捕大埔區手無寸鐵的中學生及市民」的臨時動議。(資料圖片)<br />\n<br />\n上周六大埔墟港鐵站發生多宗警員疑濫用武力個案，有警員以警棍毆打一字排開及高舉雙手的市民，亦有青年被打至頭破血流。大埔區議會社會服務委員會今日開會，新同盟周炫瑋提出「譴責警方7/9於大埔墟港鐵站毆打及拘捕大埔區手無寸鐵的中學生及市民」的臨時動議，惟全部民建聯區議員及部份建制派區議員離席，觸發流會。民主派批評建制派集體離席逃避表態，亦令不少民生議題未能於會上討論。<br />\n<br />\n大埔區議會社會服務委員會今早開會，會議至約中午12時，民建聯議員、委員會主席譚榮勳宣佈處理由周炫瑋提出，有關譴責警方於9月7日行動的動議，與此同時包括民建聯大埔區議會主席黃碧嬌在內，約10名建制派議員陸續離席，在動議提出時會議室只剩下6名民主派議員、委員會正副主席、及鄉事派鄧銘泰。由於法定人數不足，會議最終流會。<br />\n<br />\n民主派會後譴責建制派搞流會，周炫瑋批評建制派做法荒謬，怯於表達意見，「反對又唔夠膽，棄權又唔夠膽，只能夠選擇逃走，去逃避呢個議案」，批評建制派未有履行議員責任，行為與議員身份不相配。大埔區議員劉勇威怒斥建制派可恥，無視之後的民生議案，及地區撥款申請，一而再透過流會手段拒絕討論由民主派提出的議案。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190911/60033590?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190911%2F60033590%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=y6uglPlKbSLkZz%2BcPL4okaGvShGfzVnrv2JJWMS0YvQ%3D&h=05809523\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190911%2F60033590%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=f2b84446\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190911/60033590?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"f86731a26c4fb81774b435d638a10164c2426b81","tid":1561033,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:28:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"7db042f7e90e11b0100a49d53d8a4a8633f124a8","tid":1561033,"uid":258370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:29:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1a70ba987ef4faaafac19e01ac25a58a28483751","tid":1561033,"uid":267465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T15:55:12.000Z","msg":"保皇狗正垃圾"}]}